WEBVTT

11:59.760 --> 12:01.880
Five years
working your protection detail,

12:01.960 --> 12:03.800
and I never once stepped foot in here.

12:08.520 --> 12:09.920
Little Bee, what do you want?

12:10.000 --> 12:13.560
I've got a campaign meeting
in five minutes. Talk fast.

12:14.800 --> 12:18.320
You said
I could always come to you for help.

12:18.400 --> 12:19.960
I was being polite, Kara.

12:20.040 --> 12:22.920
I've lost everything. Money, hardware.

12:23.520 --> 12:25.280
I need somewhere to lie low.

12:25.360 --> 12:28.800
And cash. A clean vehicle.

12:28.880 --> 12:32.040
I can't be seen talking to you.
Not with everything I'm into.

12:32.120 --> 12:35.560
I'm funding Robert Kirby's campaign
to be PM.

12:38.080 --> 12:39.360
Now is not the time.

12:39.440 --> 12:42.360
I'm fond of you, Kara, butâ€¦

12:44.040 --> 12:44.880
I have to go now.

12:45.760 --> 12:47.280
Fuck your fondness!

12:47.360 --> 12:49.760
It took me years to work myself
into this position,

12:50.280 --> 12:52.160
and I don't have anything to show for it.

12:52.920 --> 12:55.760
I need to stay in the game. You got it?

12:57.040 --> 12:59.560
What game?
What have you got yourself into?

13:00.880 --> 13:05.120
I poisoned Martin Angelis
to use his deputy and gain some intel.

13:09.000 --> 13:11.000
His daughter has been kidnapped.

13:11.080 --> 13:13.920
If I can get her back,
he'll give me anything I want.

13:20.240 --> 13:22.520
I don't speak English.

13:56.120 --> 13:58.240
So, do we have a deal or not?

40:23.080 --> 40:26.720
I've got your file.
You're all set.

40:26.800 --> 40:29.680
Nice to see
you haven't lost your touch, Little Bee.
